## Module-Specific Behavior

### Client Manager
- Full CRUD with optimistic updates
- Search with debounce
- Bulk operations (post-MVP)
- Avatar upload support (post-MVP)

### Time Tracker
- Running timer with pause/resume
- Manual entry creation
- Timer edit/delete
- Weekly summary view
- Export timesheets (post-MVP)

### Contract Generator
- Template-based generation
- Guest + authenticated flows
- PDF export via share token
- Client auto-populate

### Invoice Generator
- Itemized line items
- Payment status tracking
- Guest + authenticated flows
- PDF export via share token
- Client auto-populate

### Income Tracker
- Period-based insights (weekly, monthly, quarterly)
- Outstanding vs. paid breakdown
- Client-level earnings
- Read-only (data-driven from invoices)

## Source of Truth

1. Token variables: app/globals.css
2. Tailwind mappings: tailwind.config.ts
3. Primitive components: components/ui
4. Workspace shell: components/workspace
5. Module composition: components/modules
6. Design system documentation: designsystem.md
7. Architecture standards (layers, registries, scalability): docs/architecture-standards.md
8. Workspace module IDs and dashboard deep-link helpers: lib/navigation/workspaceModules.ts
9. Color system reference: docs/stacklite-complete-color-system.md
10. Copilot instructions: .github/copilot-instructions.md

If conflict exists between implementation and documentation:
1. Align implementation back to tokenized foundations
2. Update documentation to reflect intentional behavior changes
3. Never silently diverge from token system
